    "biography": "<p>A zombie — an animated corpse conditioned for simple labour or security. It never tires and feels no pain, but is slow and only semi-intelligent.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Immunity to Pathogens, Immunity to Poisons, Immunity to all mana spells and similar powers (empathy, hypnotic song, illusion, etc.)</p><p><strong>Weaknesses:</strong> Allergy (Sunlight, Severe)</p><p><em>Attacks: Humanoid (uses whatever weapon it is given). Habitat: No natural habitat. Range: Observed in southern France, northeastern Spain. Body and Strength are the original body's, −1 (minimum 1) — set them to match the corpse. Essence 0; takes no wound modifiers and ignores damage until a Deadly wound incapacitates it. PAE p.31.</em></p>",
